      "content": "so if they won't be \"taken seriously\" just because of how they talk, isn't that basically saying that certain groups of people—like black scholars who use AAVE—are inherently less qualified for academia? if the \"standard\" is just how white academics talk, isn't the whole system basically biased against anyone who doesn't fit that specific mold?",
